---
title: Cherry-Glazed Pork & Cheesy Potatoes with Roast Veggie Toss & Mayo
description: Cook up a sweet cherry glaze, then use parsley as a garnish for the perfect toppings for tender seared pork loin
steaks. With a hearty side of cheesy potatoes and sweet roasted veggies, this classic meal is simple yet stunning.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
